      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BATISTA (3) went close two back before a disappointing effort over 1300m at Pinjarra last time out. Back to 1100m today is no issue as he lands here on the fresh side and he should find this a little easier than what he's been racing in. Can fire immediately for the new stable. DIRECT DEBIT (4) missed by 0.5L over 1200m at this track most recently and rates highly on the back of that effort. Drawn well again here and should get every chance for Nottle. Can go one better. RULE THE REALM (2) disappointed two back before a 6.1L defeat over this track and trip last time out. Staples replaces the apprentice hoop now and he should be able to find the front again. Will take plenty of catching. LOVESEXY (6) gets the Blinkers on today as she makes her WA debut after never featuring at Werribee on debut. Faithfull's booking is a big tick and she's not to be discounted. LE BEAU (1) can feature on resumption.",
